{"tid":2428901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳肇始：暫一人打疫苗現心悸　賠償與否需待評估是否與疫苗有關","createTime":"2021-03-02T01:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T13:55:05.000Z","uid":50386,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ce488940ff7a96aa0f8f615cdfd32ccc1fadc3be","tid":2428901,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"食物及衛生局長陳肇始指，現時暫有一名市民接種科興疫苗後出現心悸情況，他目前仍然留醫，情況穩定，醫管局會繼續跟進。<span class=\"red\">陳肇始稱，要交由衛生署、疫苗專家委員會評估是否和接種疫苗有因果關係後，才研究是否由疫苗保障基金作賠償。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/新冠疫苗｜陳肇始：暫一人打疫苗現心悸%E3%80%80賠償與否須待評估-257650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%EF%BD%9C%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%9A%E6%9A%AB%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E7%8F%BE%E5%BF%83%E6%82%B8%25E3%2580%2580%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E8%88%87%E5%90%A6%E9%A0%88%E5%BE%85%E8%A9%95%E4%BC%B0-257650&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt15KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=968cdc09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/新冠疫苗｜陳肇始：暫一人打疫苗現心悸%E3%80%80賠償與否須待評估-257650</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n調查之後發現佢係因為冇食早餐<br />\n唔關疫苗事<br />\n不予賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69677cb14d6ea9560eb4c1e7a7a58e029c34b8c","tid":2428901,"uid":42982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"之前講法係排除唔到同疫苗無關就會畀錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c179a2a499faceec411aa030706182299c331254","tid":2428901,"uid":322130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:53:52.000Z","msg":"老屈係其他問題就唔使賠，都係做戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同專家夾埋"},{"pid":"ce29ccc3488f27cfb2f45a94f48199066b143200","tid":2428901,"uid":31215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"屌你慌會認